steps.html_instructions:
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit
Restricted usage road

Take the Paros - Siros ferry
Toll road

Take the Siros - Tinos ferry
Toll road

Take the Rafina - Tinos ferry to Rafina
Toll road
Slight left to stay on Akti Andrea Papandreou
Al. Flemingk turns left and becomes Leof. Marathonos/EO54 (signs for Athina/El. Venizelos Aerodromio)

Turn right onto Periferiaki Imittou/A64 (signs for Ελευσίνα/Περιφ Υμηττός/Elefsina/Ymittos Ring)
Toll road

Take exit Y7E to merge onto Attiki Odos/A6/E94 toward ELEFSINA
Toll road
Take exit 8 to merge onto A/D Pireos Athinon Thessalonikis Evzonon/A1/E75 toward PIREAS
At Πλ. Καραϊσκάκη, take the 1st exit onto Deligiorgi

Deligiorgi turns left and becomes Pireos/P. Tsaldari
Continue to follow Pireos
